    dc:creator "Guglielmino, Adalgisa; Olmi, Massimo" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the extant Nearctic species of Dryinus Latreille 1804 group 1 (Hymenoptera: Dryinidae), with description of a new species from the USA" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219127>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219128> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219127>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Dryinus alatus, Ƥ. 1. Head in dorsal view of holotype; 2. Chela of specimen from Arizona, Nogales. 3. Enlarged claw of specimens from Arizona, Nogales (up), Michigan, Ann Arbor (mid) and Michigan, Midland Co. (down). Scale bar 0.55 mm for 1, 0, 23 mm for 2, 0.19 mm for 3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219127/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219128>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 8. 4, 5. Dryinus americanus, holotype Ƥ, head in dorsal view (4), chela (5). 6, 7. D. crawfordi, chela of holotype (6), stigmal vein of male from Massachusetts, Bedford (7). 8. D. alatus, stigmal vein of male from Arizona, Nogales. Scale bar 0.55 mm for 4, 0.25 mm for 5, 0.16 mm for 6, 0.37 mm for 7, 0.32 mm for 8." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219128/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

